      "date": "2013-08-01 23:52:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 9:\n\nMy comment was about sharing the code for managing these different files and different structures. It seems there is a lot of duplication for saving the different bookmark files that is nearly identical and only differs in some small details (e.g. A few field names). Can't we share this code and reduce our maintenance efforts in the future?",
